  "text": "The system worked as follows. a: Each AVA searched for an object independently. b: AVA 5 first detected object 1 , and agency 1 was formed. c: All AVAs except for AVA 5 were tracking object [CITATION_1] as the member-AVAs of agency 1 , while AVA 5 was searching for a new object as a freelancer-AVA. d: AVA 5 detected object 2 and generated agency 2 . e: The agency restructuring balanced the numbers of member-AVAs in agency 1 and agency 2 . f: Since no AVA could distinguish two objects, the agency unification merged agency 2 into agency 1 . g: When the targets got apart, agency 1 detected a 'new' target. Then, it activated the agency spawning protocol to generate agency 2 again for target 2 .",
